title: Obama adjusts troop levels for continuing Afghanistan mission (USAF - United States Air Force)
text: ( Source : USAF - United States Air Force ) WASHINGTON ( AFNS ) -- President Barack Obama announced at the White House Oct. 15, that he will keep U.S. troops in Afghanistan through 2016 and a lesser number into 2017 to sustain coalition efforts
